274
00:17:08,156 --> 00:17:10,560
Oh, no, no, sir. They're in good form.

275
00:17:11,051 --> 00:17:12,379
Hmm.

276
00:17:15,722 --> 00:17:18,138
Sir, I was wondering
if I could ask you a favor.

277
00:17:18,852 --> 00:17:21,855
