295
00:17:57,946 --> 00:18:00,348
Yeah, now he is,
but wait till he turns 15.

296
00:18:00,382 --> 00:18:02,544
Little commie runt will
slip through that stupid wire

297
00:18:02,569 --> 00:18:04,385
