325
00:20:47,521 --> 00:20:49,083
<i>I got Article 15'd.</i>

326
00:20:49,279 --> 00:20:51,608
<i>That's getting my rank busted to PFC</i>

327
00:20:51,642 --> 00:20:53,488
<i>for "reckless endangerment to myself</i>

328
00:20:53,513 --> 00:20:55,043
<i>and to my fellow soldiers,"</i>

329
00:20:55,068 --> 00:20:57,763
<i>like I'm the danger,
and not this messed up war.</i>

330
00:21:05,099 --> 00:21:07,300
<i>I'm not getting out of here
alive, I know that,</i>

331
00:21:07,491 --> 00:21:10,027
<i>but I'm not dying on anyone's
terms but my own.</i>

332
00:21:10,052 --> 00:21:12,497
♪ If you were a bird
and you lived very high ♪

333
00:21:13,115 --> 00:21:15,285
<i>I'm living in hell on earth, family.</i>

334
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:17,747
