of it all, I think.

359
00:22:38,682 --> 00:22:40,372
(INHALES, EXHALES)

360
00:22:40,544 --> 00:22:42,224
And even when we were little,

361
00:22:42,544 --> 00:22:44,005
I-if I got a cold...

362
00:22:45,810 --> 00:22:49,988
