perfect combo of O.J. or soup

363
00:22:50,013 --> 00:22:51,816
to make me feel better, you know?

364
00:22:51,841 --> 00:22:53,169
(CHUCKLES)

365
00:23:03,661 --> 00:23:05,568
I want to enlist, Doc.

366
00:23:07,548 --> 00:23:09,021
