00:25:14,325 --> 00:25:15,583
The lottery, I mean.

401
00:25:15,814 --> 00:25:17,224
It's not gonna happen, Nicky.

402
00:25:18,906 --> 00:25:20,318
- It might.
- It won't.

403
00:25:21,122 --> 00:25:22,240
Yeah, I know.

404
00:25:22,935 --> 00:25:24,943
- You got a plan.
